Package: ScalingFunctions
Type: Package
Title: Collection of functions for scaling of distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nikolai Knapp
Maintainer: Nikolai Knapp <nikolai.knapp@ufz.de>
Description: The package provides functions for calculating parameters and 
  moments of common probability distributions of environmental data. Further, 
  there are functions for transferring distributions across scales, random 
  sampling of arbitrary distributions and transformations of distributions.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  data.table,
  fitdistrplus,
  gstat,
  truncdist
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
